===Relation to Islam===
[[Muzaffar Iqbal]], a notable Muslim in Canada, signed the ''[[A Scientific Dissent From Darwinism|Scientific Dissent]]'' list of the [[Discovery Institute]].<ref>

{{vcite web
|last=Edis
|first=Taner
