*[http://www.evolutionnews.org/ EvolutionNews.org] Discovery Institute website tracking media coverage of intelligent design.
*[http://www.evoinfo.org/ The Evolutionary Informatics Lab]
*[http://www.idthefuture.com/ ID The Future] A multiple contributor weblog by Discovery Institute fellows.
